
## Design Choices

- Flask was chosen for its simplicity and ease of use for creating web applications.
- SQLite is used as the database for its simplicity and portability.
- The system uses a scheduled task to fetch weather data at regular intervals.
- Alerts are sent via email using SMTP.

## Future Improvements

- Implement user authentication for personalized alerts and preferences
- Add support for more cities and countries
- Enhance visualizations with more interactive charts and maps
- Implement a more robust error handling and logging system

